<% content_for :title, "준비중 - 정화의 서재" %>

<div class="coming-soon-container">
  <div class="coming-soon-content">
    <div class="coming-soon-icon">
      🚧
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="coming-soon-title">
      청소년 콘텐츠 준비중
    </h1>
    
    <p class="coming-soon-description">
      더 좋은 콘텐츠로 찾아뵙기 위해<br>
      열심히 준비하고 있습니다.
    </p>
    
    <div class="coming-soon-features">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="bi bi-book-half"></i>
        <span>청소년을 위한 특별한 동화</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="bi bi-mortarboard"></i>
        <span>교육 콘텐츠</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <i class="bi bi-star"></i>
        <span>성장 스토리</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="coming-soon-notice">
      현재 전자동화책, 구연동화, 동화만들기 콘텐츠를<br>
      먼저 즐겨보시기 바랍니다! 😊
    </p>
    
    <div class="coming-soon-actions">
      <%= link_to "전자동화책 보러가기", courses_path(category: 'ebook'), class: "btn-coming-soon btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "구연동화 보러가기", courses_path(category: 'storytelling'), class: "btn-coming-soon btn-secondary" %>
      <%= link_to "홈으로", root_path, class: "btn-coming-soon btn-outline" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .coming-soon-container {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
  }
  
  .coming-soon-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    text-align: center;
    background: white;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .coming-soon-icon {
    font-size: 5rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
  }
  
  .coming-soon-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .coming-soon-description {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #718096;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .coming-soon-features {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: #667eea;
  }
  
  .feature-item i {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
  
  .feature-item span {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .coming-soon-notice {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #718096;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #f7fafc;
    border-radius: 12px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .coming-soon-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon.btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    border: none;
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon.btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon.btn-secondary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
    color: white;
    border: none;
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon.btn-secondary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(245, 87, 108, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon.btn-outline {
    background: white;
    color: #667eea;
    border: 2px solid #667eea;
  }
  
  .btn-coming-soon.btn-outline:hover {
    background: #667eea;
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  /* 모바일 반응형 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .coming-soon-content {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
    
    .coming-soon-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .coming-soon-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .coming-soon-features {
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .feature-item i {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .feature-item span {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    
    .coming-soon-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .btn-coming-soon {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>

